 </a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw_/jsml.htm\">教师名录</a>\n                &gt;\n                正文\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw_/szgk.htm\" title=\"师资概况\">师资概况</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szdw_/jsml.htm\" title=\"教师名录\">教师名录</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<ul class=\"banner-ul pull-right tabs-ul clearfix\">\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/F/CD/1D/985E2B0C584F5713C0467978970_D2294B9C_1D8C0.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>王博</a>副教授</div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                     \n                              \n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                \n               \n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n \n\n\n   \n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"wow fadeInUp sznr\"><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">个人介绍</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p>姓名：王博</p>\n<p>职称：副教授</p>\n<p>邮箱：<a href=\"mailto:wangbo2019@tsinghua.edu.cn\">wangbo2019@tsinghua.edu.cn</a></p>\n<p>主页地址：<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://bowangthu.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\">https://bowangthu.github.io/</a></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">教育背景</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">工学博士（计算机科学与技术），清华大学，中国，2014.9-2019.7</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">工学学士（计算机科学与技术），北京邮电大学，中国，2010.9-2014.7</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">工作履历</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">副教授、助理教授，博士生导师，清华大学，中国，2021.11-今</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">博士后， 清华大学，中国，2019.7-2021.11</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">研究领域</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">网络传输，视频实时传输</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">研究概况</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 长期从事互联网视频实时传输、网络传输协议、传输安全的研究。以点播、直播、实时视频通信等为典型应用场景，研究提升视频传输实时性与安全性的相关理论和方法。研究成果发表在ACM SIGCOMM，USENIX NSDI，ACM MM，IEEE/ACM TON，IEEE TMC等国际会议/期刊上，并广泛应用于阿里、字节、华为、腾讯、快手等知名企业的核心业务。研究成果获得中国通信学会技术发明一等奖 2 项。</span><br></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">社会兼职</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">APAN Board of Director<br>Workshop Chair: SIGCOMM N2Women 2023，SIGCOMM EMS 2025<br>Publication Chair: PRDC 2022<br>TPC member：MM（2021-2025）</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">奖励与荣誉</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">中国科协青年人才托举工程 <br>Top 10 N2Women Rising Stars in Computer Networking and Communications<br>世界互联网大会“全球青年领军者”（首批）<br>清华大学“水木学者”（首批）</span></p></div></div><div class=\"post post1 clearfix\"> <div class=\"tt\"><div class=\"title\">学术成果</div></div> <div class=\"con\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">1. Bo Wang, Xingxing Yang, Zili Meng, Yaning Guo, Chen Sun, Justine Sherry, Hongqiang Harry Liu, Mingwei Xu, Jianping Wu, “Zhuge: Towards Consistent Low Latency with Minimal Control Loop Delay”, IEEE/ACM TON, 2024.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">2. Bo Wang, Muhan Su, Wufan Wang, Kefan Chen, Bingyang Liu, Fengyuan Ren, Mingwei Xu, Jiangchuan Liu, Jianping Wu, “Enhancing Low Latency Adaptive Live Streaming Through Precise Bandwidth Prediction”, IEEE/ACM TON, 2024.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">3. Zili Meng, Xiao Kong, Jing Chen, Bo Wang*, Mingwei Xu, Rui Han, Honghao Liu, Venkat Arun, Hongxin Hu, Xue Wei, “Hairpin: Rethinking Packet Loss Recovery in Edge-based Interactive Video Streaming”, USENIX NSDI, 2024.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">4. Jing Chen, Bo Wang, Zhiyuan Xu, Yan Zhang, Minhu Wang, Mingwei Xu, Zili Meng, “Bidirectional Bandwidth Coordination under Half-Duplex Bottlenecks for Video Streaming”, IEEE ICNP, 2024. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">5. Kefan Chen, Bo Wang, Wufan Wang, Xiaoyu Li, Fengyuan Ren, “DeeProphet: Improving HTTP Adaptive Streaming for Low Latency Live Video by Meticulous Bandwidth Prediction”, ACM WWW, 2023.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">6. Zili Meng, Yaning Guo, Chen Sun, Bo Wang*, Justine Sherry, Hongqiang Harry Liu, Mingwei Xu, “Achieving Consistent Low Latency for Wireless Real-Time Communications with the Shortest Control Loop”, ACM SIGCOMM, 2022.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">7. Bo Wang, Mingwei Xu, Fengyuan Ren, Jianping Wu, “Cratus: a Lightweight and Robust Approach for Mobile Live Streaming”, IEEE TMC, 2022. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">8. Wufan Wang, Bo Wang, Lei Zhang, Hua Huang, “Sensitivity-aware Spatial Quality Adaptation for Live Video Analytics”, IEEE JSAC, 2022.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">9. Bo Wang, Mingwei Xu, Fengyuan Ren, Jianping Wu, “Improving Robustness of DASH Against Unpredictable Network Variations”, IEEE TMM, 2021. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">10. Bo Wang, Fengyuan Ren, Jiahai Yang, Chao Zhou, “Improving the Performance of Online Bitrate Adaptation with Multi-step Prediction over Cellular Networks”, IEEE TMC, 2019. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 12px;\">11. Bo Wang, Fengyuan Ren, “Towards Forward-looking Online Bitrate Adaptation for DASH”, ACM MM, 2017. (Oral, Acceptance rate 7.5%) </span><br></p></div></div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    </form>\n\n<style>\n.container p span {\n    font-size: 16px !important;}\n\n.container p {\n    font-size: 16px !important;}\n.article-txt p {\n    margin-left:0!important;\n    margin-right:0!important;}\n\n.article-txt p,.article-txt p span {\n    font-size: 17px!important;}\n.vsbcontent_img{text-align: center;}\ntable {font-size: 16px;}table{display: flex;overflow: auto hidden; white-space: nowrap;word-break: keep-all;width:100%!important;}\n@media(max-width: 860px) {\n.article-txt p img {\n    margin: 0 auto!important;\n    height: auto!important;}\n}\n</style>\n<script>\nfunction contentFix(){\n    var Width = window.innerWidth;\n    if( Width < 768){\n      $(\"#vsb_content .vsbcontent_img img\").each(function(){\n          $(this).css({\"height\":\"auto\"});     \n      });\n      $(\"#vsb_content .img_